reply_text:
@Joeghost47 Yes that mean that Jeremy Renner is not playing himself. 

When an actor plays themselves it means they keep their real name and characteristics, often exaggerating certain parts of their personality. 

There was a theory going around that since Jeremy Renner was known to exist within the knives out universe he would be playing himself as the actor/character Jeremy Renner. Instead he will be playing the character called Nat Sharp
